Structure

Class Structure

  • java.lang.Object
    • Structure.Structure

  • public class Structure
extends java.lang.Object
    Object representation of the card object structure. Each structure has a name, color, age in which the structure appears, an associated resource cost, a list of effects the structure provides when constructed, the number of copies, and a structure if completed satisfies the resource cost. See page xx for more information.
